doc ///
    Key
        (degree, ComplexMap)
    Headline
        get the degree of a map of chain complexes
    Usage
        degree f
    Inputs
        f:ComplexMap
    Outputs
        :ZZ
    Description
        Text
            A complex map $f : C \to D$ of degree $d$ is a sequence of
            of maps $f_i : C_i \to D_{i+d}$.
            This method returns $d$.
        Text
            The degree of the differential of a complex is always -1.
